013">が</span><span begin="3:18.013" end="3:18.888">頬</span><span begin="3:18.888" end="3:19.672">を</span><span begin="3:19.672" end="3:21.184">伝</span><span begin="3:21.184" end="3:22.269">う</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">只是在渴求着 热泪却从脸颊上滑落</span></p><p begin="3:22.269" end="3:24.299" itunes:key="L21" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="3:22.269" end="3:22.304">言</span><span begin="3:22.304" end="3:22.420">い</span><span begin="3:22.420" end="3:22.656">た</span><span begin="3:22.656" end="3:22.727">い</span><span begin="3:22.727" end="3:22.939">こ</span><span begin="3:22.939" end="3:23.012">と</span><span begin="3:23.012" end="3:23.076">な</span><span begin="3:23.076" end="3:23.399">ん</span><span begin="3:23.399" end="3:23.476">か</span><span begin="3:23.476" end="3:23.543">無</span><span begin="3:23.543" end="3:24.299">い</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">没有什么想说的话</span></p><p begin="3:24.299" end="3:30.685" itunes:key="L22" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="3:24.299" end="3:24.521">た</span><span begin="3:24.521" end="3:24.801">だ</span><span begin="3:24.801" end="3:25.081">も</span><span begin="3:25.081" end="3:25.254">う</span><span begin="3:25.254" end="3:25.494">一</span><span begin="3:25.494" end="3:25.673">度</span><span begin="3:25.673" end="3:26.198">会</span><span begin="3:26.198" end="3:26.397">い</span><span begin="3:26.397" end="3:27.174">た</span><span begin="3:27.174" end="3:30.685">い</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">只是想再相见一次</span></p><p begin="3:30.685" end="3:32.749" itunes:key="L23" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="3:30.685" end="3:30.813">言</span><span begin="3:30.813" end="3:30.989">い</span><span begin="3:30.989" end="3:31.105">た</span><span begin="3:31.105" end="3:31.245">い</span><span begin="3:31.245" end="3:31.313">こ</span><span begin="3:31.313" end="3:31.640">と</span><span begin="3:31.640" end="3:31.853">言</span><span begin="3:31.853" end="3:31.956">え</span><span begin="3:31.956" end="3:32.072">な</span><span b